### 6. Multi-stage Builds
**Rule:** Use multi-stage builds for production images.
```dockerfile
# Build stage
FROM node:22-alpine AS builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci --only=production

# Runtime stage
FROM node:22-alpine
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=builder /app/node_modules ./node_modules
COPY . .
CMD ["node", "index.js"]
```
